In the Spring of 2025 I took a class Quantative Reasoning class based in R. I wrote some code, and did some cool data science. Here is a collection of links!

I am so proud of how much I have learned so far, and I am excited to see how to advance through the semester.

Some of my favorite past times include thrifting, sewing, up-cycling, cooking/baking, and going to art museums. I look forward to displaying my academic accomplishments on this website that I created myself using code!
